Ruxshona ERP UI - Fayl Tuzilmasi, Loyiha Maqsadi va Printer Diagnostika
======================================================================

Yangilangan sana: 2026-02-25
Repo: ruxshona-erp-ui

1) Loyiha maqsadi
-----------------
Bu loyiha "Ruxshona Tort" korxonasi uchun ERP desktop/web interfeysini beradi.
Asosiy vazifalar:
- Sotuv (POS) va chek chiqarish
- Ishlab chiqarish va label (barcode) chop etish
- Ombor kirim/chiqim, transfer, vazvrat
- Filial/do'kon boshqaruvi
- Xarajatlar, ish haqi, hisobotlar
- Website platformasi uchun buyurtmalar/custom request/coupon boshqaruvi
- Rollar va ruxsatlar (admin, sales, production va boshqalar)

2) Arxitektura (qisqa)
----------------------
- Frontend: Next.js App Router (src/app)
- UI komponentlar: src/components
- Business servislar (API bilan ishlash): src/services
- Utility va state helperlar: src/lib
- Desktop qismi: Tauri (src-tauri)
- Auto-update release oqimi: releases/ + scripts/create-updater-manifest.mjs

