7) Printerga aloqador joylar (aniq)
-----------------------------------
A) Frontend (TypeScript)
- src/lib/desktop-printer.ts
  - Printer rejimlari: RECEIPT / LABEL
  - Ro'yxat olish: listDesktopPrinters()
  - Default o'rnatish: setDesktopDefaultPrinter()
  - Auto tanlash: ensureDefaultPrinterForMode(), autoConfigureDefaultPrinterForRole(), autoConfigureDefaultPrinterForContext()
  - Local saqlash: desktop_printer_receipt, desktop_printer_label
  - Hozirgi prioritet nomlar: RUX_RECEIPT va RUX_LABEL

- src/app/sales/sell/page.tsx
  - Chek printer dropdown
  - "Chek chiqarilsin" flag
  - printCurrentWindowWithPrinter() orqali receipt print

- src/components/pos/Receipt.tsx
  - Receipt print CSS
  - Print izolatsiya: body[data-receipt-print="1"] orqali faqat receipt ko'rinadi
  - @page size qog'oz eniga bog'langan (paperWidthMm)

- src/app/production/entry/page.tsx
  - Ishlab chiqarish label print logikasi
  - Har bir label alohida page konteynerda chiqariladi
  - Pop-up print (fallback iframe)

- src/app/ikpu/page.tsx
  - Barcode label print logikasi
  - Printdan oldin LABEL printer ensure qilinadi

- src/app/settings/receipt/page.tsx
  - Label va chek shabloni sozlamalari:
    - paperWidthMm
    - labelWidthMm / labelHeightMm
    - labelBarcodeWidthMm / labelBarcodeHeightMm
    - showLabelProductionDate va boshqa flaglar

B) Desktop bridge (Rust / Tauri)
- src-tauri/src/lib.rs
  - list_printers (PowerShell orqali)
  - get_default_printer
  - set_default_printer
  - PowerShell hidden/no-window rejimida ishlaydi (CREATE_NO_WINDOW)

- src-tauri/tauri.conf.json
  - additionalBrowserArgs ichida --kiosk-printing bor
  - bu print dialogsiz avtomatik printga yordam beradi

C) Windows tomoni (OS/Driver)
- Printer nomlari amalda standartlashtirilgan:
  - RUX_RECEIPT (chek printer)
  - RUX_LABEL (label printer)
- Windows default auto-manage o'chirilgan bo'lishi kerak:
  - LegacyDefaultPrinterMode = 1

8) Oxirgi kuzatilgan xatoliklar va holati
-----------------------------------------
1) Ishlab chiqarishda sotuv cheki chiqib ketishi
- Sabab: global receipt print CSS ishlab chiqarish print contextga aralashishi.
- Tuzatish: Receipt CSS body[data-receipt-print="1"] bilan cheklangan.
- Holat: Kod darajasida tuzatilgan.

2) Label eniga/aylangan holatda (landscape) chiqib ketishi
- Sabab: driver orientation yoki page context nomosligi.
- Tuzatish: label printda alohida page wrapper ishlatildi; popup contextga chiqarildi.
- Holat: Kod darajasida tuzatilgan, lekin driver sozlamasi ham shart.
- Driver talabi: Orientation=Portrait, Scale=100%, Paper size appdagi mm bilan bir xil.

3) Label matni bir nechta stiker orasiga siljib ketishi
- Sabab: continuous media + gap calibration noto'g'ri yoki page break nomos.
- Tuzatish: har label alohida page/height bilan chop etiladi.
- Holat: Kod tuzatildi; printerda Gap/Label calibration qilish kerak.

4) Sotuvda printerga hech narsa ketmasligi
- Sabab: noto'g'ri default printer yoki OS default auto-switch konflikti.
- Tuzatish: RUX_RECEIPT prioritet, auto-manage off, stored printer qo'llanadi.
- Holat: Kodda tuzatilgan; foydalanuvchi muhitida dropdownda to'g'ri printer tanlanganini tekshirish kerak.

5) Login/open paytida blocking popup/alert chiqishi
- Sabab: eski alert logic.
- Tuzatish: blocking alert olib tashlangan.
- Holat: Tuzatilgan.

9) Tezkor diagnostika checklist (printer)
-----------------------------------------
1. Get-Printer bilan RUX_RECEIPT va RUX_LABEL borligini tekshirish.
2. LegacyDefaultPrinterMode=1 ekanini tekshirish.
3. Sales sahifasida receipt dropdown -> RUX_RECEIPT.
4. Production sahifasida label dropdown -> RUX_LABEL.
5. Label printer driverda paper size/orientation/scale/gap sensor sozlamasi to'g'ri ekanini tekshirish.

